Why can't you understand that?

6
00:00:22,879 --> 00:00:24,320
The goods I'm delivering right now

7
00:00:24,399 --> 00:00:25,519
will be paid for soon.

8
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:26,879
Once they're sold,

9
00:00:26,960 --> 00:00:28,239
we'll have money.

10
00:00:28,239 --> 00:00:29,079
So what?

11
00:00:29,519 --> 00:00:31,559
You say that so confidently every time,

12
00:00:31,580 --> 00:00:33,100
but you blow it on booze and gambling

13
00:00:33,120 --> 00:00:34,110
whenever you get money.

14
00:00:34,140 --> 00:00:35,800
Have you ever sent a single dime home?

15
00:00:35,920 --> 00:00:36,709
No more dreaming!

16
00:00:36,710 --> 00:00:37,780
I won't give you anything!

17
00:00:38,360 --> 00:00:39,880
You're not doing me this favor, huh?

18
00:00:40,660 --> 00:00:42,040
I'm telling you, when I get rich,

19
00:00:42,060 --> 00:00:43,660
the first thing I'll do is divorce you!

20
00:00:43,660 --> 00:00:44,840
You wench!

21
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:50,039
Divorce her right now if you can.

22
00:00:50,200 --> 00:00:50,960
You wretched woman.

23
00:00:50,960 --> 00:00:52,439
How dare you hit me?

24
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:05,920
My head hurts.

25
00:01:06,280 --> 00:01:07,439
I must have a concussion.

26
00:01:08,280 --> 00:01:09,159
You have to pay me.

27
00:01:09,760 --> 00:01:11,800
Listen, I'll call the police
if you don't pay me.

28
00:01:13,719 --> 00:01:14,280
Pay me money.

29
00:01:16,879 --> 00:01:17,680
I'm dizzy.

30
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:25,680
Get lost.

31
00:01:26,439 --> 00:01:27,920
Take the money and scram.

32
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:37,079
You have no shame.

33
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:41,640
Dear,

34
00:01:42,719 --> 00:01:44,159
I'll wait for you outside after work.

35
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:51,760
Dear.

36
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,319
I'm not going with you.

37
00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:58,079
You think

38
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,719
that woman will keep protecting you?

39
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,079
You know what?

40
00:02:01,319 --> 00:02:02,519
She can't even protect herself

41
00:02:02,519 --> 00:02:03,480
right now.

42
00:02:05,719 --> 00:02:06,719
What do you mean?

43
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:11,919
You're too nosy.

44
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,159
Beat her.

45
00:02:13,500 --> 00:02:14,400
See for yourself.

46
00:02:20,660 --> 00:02:21,940
Are you out of your mind?

